OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774605947
OL,3,COwner 'did not think dog which savaged
OL,4,Cpensioner was aggressive'
OL,6,FThe owner of an XL bully which savaged
OL,7,Fa pensioner "as if he were its prey"
OL,8,Fhas told a court he would not have had
OL,9,Fit around his children if he thought
OL,10,Fit was aggressive.
OL,12,FJohn McColl, 84, died from his
OL,13,Finjuries a month after the attack by
OL,14,Fthe dog, which had to be shot 10 times
OL,15,Fby armed police officers who were
OL,16,Fcalled to the scene in Warrington,
OL,17,FCheshire, in February 2025.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
