OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774605947
OL,3,COwner 'did not think dog which savaged
OL,4,Cpensioner was aggressive'
OL,6,FGiving evidence at Liverpool Crown
OL,7,FCourt, owner Sean Garner said he took
OL,8,Fsteps to stop his dog, Toretto, and a
OL,9,Ffemale XL bully called Malibu from
OL,10,Fbeing dangerously out of control.
OL,12,FHe said before leaving the house on 24
OL,13,FFebruary, he had locked Toretto in a
OL,14,Fshed in the backyard, which was
OL,15,Fsecured by a gate with a latch and a
OL,16,Fchain which acted as a bolt.
OL,18,FThe jury has heard Mr McColl was
OL,19,Fattacked just after 6pm when he
OL,20,Fwandered into the driveway on Bardsley
OL,21,FAvenue.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774605947
OL,3,COwner 'did not think dog which savaged
OL,4,Cpensioner was aggressive'
OL,6,FGarner, 31, told the court he had
OL,7,Fowned Toretto for about four-and-a-
OL,8,Fhalf years, since the dog was between
OL,9,Ffour and six months old.
OL,11,FHe said: "His behaviour was brilliant.
OL,13,F"If my dog showed aggression, I
OL,14,Fwouldn't have had the dog around my
OL,15,Fkids.
OL,17,F"I've got a family. I've got people
OL,18,Fwho would have stepped in if they
OL,19,Fthought the dog was aggressive."
OL,26,@sD@JOUuD@AOUyD@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774605947
OL,3,COwner 'did not think dog which savaged
OL,4,Cpensioner was aggressive'
OL,6,FHe said the dog was "perfect" around
OL,7,Fother dogs, and fine with people.
OL,9,FLloyd Morgan, defending, asked Garner
OL,10,Fabout a message he sent to his mother
OL,11,Fin March 2024, in which he described
OL,12,Fthe dog as "missing a few nuts and
OL,13,Fbolts".
OL,15,FHe said: "He's 100mph. He was always
OL,16,Fexcited when he saw my mum. He knew he
OL,17,Fwas either getting treats or he was
OL,18,Fgoing out.
OL,26,@nD@UOUnD@]O]tD@LOUuD@FO]wD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774605947
OL,3,COwner 'did not think dog which savaged
OL,4,Cpensioner was aggressive'
OL,6,F"It was a figure of speech. I weren't
OL,7,Fmeaning that my dog's aggressive, I
OL,8,Fwas meaning he is 100mph."
OL,10,FHe said at the time he had not
OL,11,Fbelieved either of his dogs were XL
OL,12,Fbullies, a banned breed which can only
OL,13,Fbe owned with an exemption
OL,14,Fcertificate, although he now accepted
OL,15,Fthey were.
OL,17,FThe court heard he had an Instagram
OL,18,Fpage, called Little and Large Bullies,
OL,19,Fwhich he used to promote dogs for
OL,20,Fbreeding.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774605947
OL,3,COwner 'did not think dog which savaged
OL,4,Cpensioner was aggressive'
OL,6,FHe agreed he had advertised Malibu for
OL,7,Fbreeding as an XL bully, but said that
OL,8,Fwas because it was easier to sell
OL,9,Fpuppies from that breed.
OL,11,FHe said he had not bred Toretto with
OL,12,Fhis own dogs, but had used him as a
OL,13,Fstud for other people.
OL,15,FGarner, who the court heard had
OL,16,Fprevious convictions for driving
OL,17,Foffences and drugs possession with
OL,18,Fintent to supply, said he was self-
OL,19,Femployed and ran a recovery business
OL,20,Ftransporting cars.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774605947
OL,3,COwner 'did not think dog which savaged
OL,4,Cpensioner was aggressive'
OL,6,FHe said he had previously worked in a
OL,7,Fdog fertility clinic, helping with
OL,8,Fcollection of semen and "analysis to
OL,9,Fmake sure they had enough swimmers".
OL,11,FHe moved into the home in the Dallam
OL,12,Farea of Warrington with his then-
OL,13,Fpregnant partner and their two
OL,14,Fchildren about three weeks before Mr
OL,15,FMcColl was attacked, the jury was told,
OL,17,FHe accepted he did not tell the truth
OL,18,Fwhen he moved in and told the landlord
OL,19,Fhe had one French bulldog, rather than
OL,20,Fthe two XL bullys and one micro bully
OL,21,Fdog which he owned.
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774605947
OL,3,COwner 'did not think dog which savaged
OL,4,Cpensioner was aggressive'
OL,6,FHe said: "I was trying to better my
OL,7,Flife. Some landlords discriminate
OL,8,Fagainst dogs and don't let you get the
OL,9,Fproperty."
OL,11,FGarner, now of Belle Vale, Liverpool,
OL,12,Fdenies being the owner of a dog which
OL,13,Fcaused injury while dangerously out of
OL,14,Fcontrol.
OL,26,@nD@JOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
